sys_hub_action_type_definition.annotation: Queues the execution of the defined plan in Bamboo.
sys_hub_action_type_definition.description: At a minimum you have to provide the Bamboo project and plan keys. In this case the plan executes up to the first manual stage. If you want to execute manual stages as well, you have to specifiy the stage up to which you want to execute the plan. You can execute all stages with the flag "Execute All Bambpo Stages". By default always the latest revision from source control is built. You can specify a specific revision with the input parameter " VCS Revision".
sys_hub_action_type_definition.name: Execute Bamboo Plan
